title: UNLOCKED! Time Keeps On Dippin' Into The Future with Alan Trong
itunes:title: UNLOCKED! Time Keeps On Dippin' Into The Future with Alan Trong
description:
On this episode of The Doughboys Double, Alan Trong (Alita: Battle Angel, Daybreak, The Tomorrow War) joins the ‘boys for his first-ever podcast appearance and talks Vietnamese eats and throwback meals before a Dippin’ Dots taste test.
